{"tid":2303994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總加速師又出招：興建雅魯藏布江下游大壩惹怒印度和南亞國家","createTime":"2020-11-28T11:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T07:25:19.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd4944ab0800fe5397707ae8ce7929357f2187f","tid":2303994,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"中國敲定雅魯藏布江下游水電開發<br />\n最新更新：2020/11/28 18:32<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北28日電）<span class=\"red\">中國電力建設集團董事長晏志勇近日證實，中國將實施「雅魯藏布江下游水電開發」，預計發電量將超過世界規模最大的三峽電站。但這項計劃可能再挑起雅魯藏布江流域周邊國家的敏感神經。</span><br />\n<br />\n據中國能源報報導，晏志勇近日出席中國水力發電工程學會成立40週年紀念大會時提到，中共黨中央制定「十四五規劃」和「2035年遠景目標」，明確提出「實施雅魯藏布江下游水電開發」。<br />\n<br />\n他還強調「實施」二字，證實這項開發案已敲定，並稱這是一項「國家安全工程」，包含水資源及中國的國土安全等。<br />\n<br />\n晏志勇表示，雅魯藏布江流域的水能源，理論蘊藏量近8000萬瓩。其中，下游的「大拐彎地區」在50公里的直線距離內形成2000公尺的落差，匯集近7000萬瓩的技術可開發資源，規模超過3個三峽電站（裝機容量2250萬瓩）。<br />\n<br />\n他並稱，雅魯藏布江下游水電近6000萬瓩水電開發後，每年可提供近3000億度低碳電力；水電站運作後，也可為西藏自治區帶來人民幣200億元（約新台幣870億元）以上的財政收入。<br />\n<br />\n晏志勇還宣稱，這是一項「國際合作」工程，將使中國與南亞國家的合作更加暢通。<br />\n<br />\n據公開資料，<span class=\"red\">雅魯藏布江是中國坡度最陡的大河，流域包含中印主權爭議的邊境地帶，也就是中國聲稱的「藏南地區」。此外，中印兩國也曾就雅魯藏布江流域的水文資料共享、修建水壩等議題發生爭執。</span>（編輯：賴言曦/楊昇儒）1091128<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202011280175.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202011280175.aspx&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=013c779f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202011280175.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"fe17cd51773f1d8bc994732aceff65595e58c85a","tid":2303994,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"中國：印度本身已經係敵人，洗鬼理佢感受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb03979b433a1fc60b364ae96f6fe1a1597ec085","tid":2303994,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">老鳳懷疑張奕鈞先生(SimonTW #337052)為在台共諜</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2e53ad12d8c00023954c8cc957eee400974d9d9","tid":2303994,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e55625e6bebad26052e98e2c6901ac4a200b91","tid":2303994,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國擬在雅魯藏布江下游實施水電開發 規模相當於3個三峽電站</span></strong><br />\n     2020-11-28 14:35 列印 文字大小<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/c8a52edc7b2dd207b97a3a3131c5b247/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201128/_2020112814375332330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fc8a52edc7b2dd207b97a3a3131c5b247%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201128%2F_2020112814375332330.jpg&h=adff0b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國擬在雅魯藏布江下游實施水電開發，規模相當於3個三峽電站。網圖<br />\n<br />\n中央制定「十四五」規劃及2035年遠景目標，當中明確提出實施西藏雅魯藏布江下游水電開發，<span class=\"red\">中國電力建設集團有限公司董事長晏志勇強調將全力落實，預計規模相當於3個多的三峽電站</span>，又形容將會是涉及水資源及國土安全的國家安全工程項目。<br />\n<br />\n晏志勇指出，雅魯藏布江下游近6000萬千瓦水電，規模相當於3個多三峽電站，每年可提供近3000億度清潔、可再生、零碳的電力，可為國家爭取在2060年前實現「碳中和」。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，作為國內「西電東送」的能源接續基地，西藏自治區目前水電資源的開發程度極低，僅為技術可開發量的1%左右，因此雅魯藏布江下游水電的開發，必將對西藏自治區的經濟社會發展，以及國家能源電力行業發展有重大歷史意義和現實意義。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1935526/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%85%E9%AD%AF%E8%97%8F%E5%B8%83%E6%B1%9F%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%B8%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%B0%B4%E9%9B%BB%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%95%B6%E6%96%BC3%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1935526%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%259B%2585%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B1%259F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2596%25BC3%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%2599&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=fb7fc73f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1935526%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%259B%2585%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B1%259F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2596%25BC3%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%2599&h=6fcfa188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1935526/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%85%E9%AD%AF%E8%97%8F%E5%B8%83%E6%B1%9F%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%B8%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%B0%B4%E9%9B%BB%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC-%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%95%B6%E6%96%BC3%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%99</a>"},{"pid":"e8ebcd04722533847a65565e4ffd452b612fb56e","tid":2303994,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/28/realtime/9156422.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F28%2Frealtime%2F9156422.png%2